      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I am not implying that cultural diversity diminishes prestige; rather, the specific vocabulary I used for Option B—such as \"vibrant\" and \"soulful\"—is often associated with a more dynamic, less formal atmosphere that can feel less refined in the traditional luxury market. In the context of a high-end brochure, \"timeless elegance\" signals a stable, established prestige, whereas \"soulful\" might be perceived as trendy or informal. This is a matter of tone and perception rather than an inherent quality of the neighborhood.",
